* Create\nManaged Tables
** Default table type in Unity Catalog
***_ Databricks manages metadata + data files
** Delta Lake format by default
***_ ACID transactions
***_ Time travel
***_ Schema enforcement
** Using SQL
***_ CREATE TABLE with column definitions
***_ USE CATALOG / USE SCHEMA for context
** Advanced features
***_ Constraints: enforce data quality rules
***_ Generated columns: auto-computed values
** Lifecycle management
***_ Drop table = delete metadata + data files
@endmindmap
